explains: adj. [解剖] 子宫的；同母异父的

sentences.en: This is the uterus down here, sort of half of it is shown with the uterine wall, the fallopian tubes, and the ovaries.
sentences.cn: 下面这个是子宫，大概有一半是子宫壁、输卵管和卵巢。

sentences.en: Uterine hypocontractility should be augmented after both the maternal pelvis and fetal presentation have been assessed.
sentences.cn: 在对母体骨盆和胎儿先露都进行评估后，低张性子宫收缩应加以强化。

sentences.en: Meanwhile related factors of uterine infection were investigated.
sentences.cn: 同时调查与宫内感染的有关因素。
